  "body": "Using react v0.14.0-beta3 and react-overlay's Modal (which uses Portal). Portal is using `renderSubtreeIntoContainer`. It appears that test utils are not aware of subtrees rendered in containers, so when you search for children they don't get crawled.\n\nThis means that in order to test my components I have to first get `instance.refs.modal`, instead of being able to use TestUtils directly.\n\nI looked up related discussions and wasn't able to find anything on this. Are there plans to make test utils aware of this feature? It'd be a nice convenience.\n",
